    "インタビューや取材向け。声の明瞭さを重視した高品質な設定です。": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "For interviews and reporting. High-quality settings prioritizing voice clarity."
          }
        },
